    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I feel like I'm being pulled in two directions. Lately, I've been having these incredibly clear signs—sometimes in dreams, sometimes just a feeling in my chest—that I've been chosen to protect our traditional way of life. It’s like I’m a guardian for everything our ancestors built, but the modern world is just trying to tear it all down through these new laws and secular movements. It feels like a sacred duty, but it's so heavy. Can you help me understand if this is a real spiritual calling or if I'm just losing my mind?",
